      <p><strong>Last updated: January 2025</strong></p>
      <p>O2Taxi ("we", "us", "our") is a taxi and private hire service based in Thame, Oxfordshire. This privacy policy explains how we collect and use information when you contact us or use our services.</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you book a taxi or contact us, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name and phone number</li>
        <li>Your pickup address and destination</li>
        <li>Journey date and time</li>
        <li>Flight or train details where provided</li>
        <li>Any other information you voluntarily share with us</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information you provide solely to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Confirm and fulfil your taxi booking</li>
        <li>Contact you about your journey</li>
        <li>Provide you with your driver's details before pickup</li>
        <li>Respond to any queries or complaints</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not use your information for marketing purposes without your explicit consent, and we do not sell your data to third parties.</p>

      <h2>3. WhatsApp and Phone Communications</h2>
      <p>When you contact us via WhatsApp or phone, your message content and contact details are visible to us. WhatsApp messages are subject to WhatsApp's own privacy policy (whatsapp.com/legal). We recommend reviewing their policy if you have concerns.</p>

      <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your booking information for a reasonable period to handle any queries or disputes relating to your journey, after which it is securely deleted.</p>

      <h2>5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
      <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties except where necessary to fulfil your booking (for example, passing your pickup details to your assigned driver).</p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us via WhatsApp on 07923 360048 or by calling us directly.</p>

      <h2>7. Cookies and Website</h2>
      <p>Our website (o2taxi.com) does not use tracking cookies or analytics services that collect personal data. We use Google Fonts which may set a cookie – you can block this in your browser settings if preferred.</p>

      <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please contact us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Phone / WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="tel:+447923360048">07923 360048</a></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@o2taxi.com">info@o2taxi.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Thame, Oxfordshire, OX9</li>
      </ul>
